    "created_at": "2014-02-11T04:50:45Z",
    "updated_at": "2014-02-11T04:50:45Z",
    "body": "That logic will restore the correct `--out-dir` behavior, but it will not have the correct build behavior. We changed it to output by default to the current directory, not to the directory holding the source file (which is what the old logic did).\n",
